Name: Fantasy Mosaics 33: Inventor's Workshop
About the game: Fantasy Mosaics 33 is a new installment of multi-color mosaics puzzles based on pixel art images. The gameplay is an original variation of the popular picross or nonogram genre. The app features innovative mini games and a wizard's workshop to explore.
